        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Overconfidence bias from previous successful inspections, which might create false confidence in the inspection process despite recent failures.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Weller found that good code inspection results can create false confidence.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Inspection personnel background bias, as his manager doubts the inspection personnel's necessary background, which might affect inspection effectiveness.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "John has been using design inspections on his projects since he came to his current employer, even though his manager does not believe that the inspection personnel have the necessary background to be successful.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
