        "segment": "To calculate the MMRE (Mean Magnitude of Relative Error), we first compute the relative error for each project as the absolute value of (estimate - actual) divided by actual.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "MMRE is the mean magnitude of relative error, so we hope that the MMRE for a particular model is very small.",
                "img_id": null
            }
