[
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "To determine the critical path, we calculate the total duration for each path from milestone A to milestone J by summing the durations of the activities along each path.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Analyzing the paths among the milestones of a project in this way is called the Critical Path Method (CPM) . The paths can show us the minimum amount of time it will take to complete the project, given our estimates of each activity's duration.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet_intro",
        "segment": "Calculations for each path are as follows:",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Path ACFHJ: A→C (6 days) + C→F (4 days) + F→H (20 days) + H→J (10 days) = 6 + 4 + 20 + 10 = 40 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Path ACFIHJ: A→C (6 days) + C→F (4 days) + F→I (4 days) + I→H (1 day) + H→J (10 days) = 6 + 4 + 4 + 1 + 10 = 25 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Path ABEGHJ: A→B (3 days) + B→E (15 days) + E→G (2 days) + G→J (7 days) = 3 + 15 + 2 + 7 = 27 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "Path ADFHJ: A→D (10 days) + D→F (8 days) + F→H (20 days) + H→J (10 days) = 10 + 8 + 20 + 10 = 48 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The critical path is the path with the longest total duration, which determines the minimum time to complete the project. From the calculations, path ADFHJ has the longest duration of 48 days.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "The longest path has a slack of zero for each of its nodes, because it is the path that determines whether or not the project is on schedule. For this reason, it is called the critical path.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "Therefore, the critical path from milestone A to milestone J is ADFHJ.",
        "citations": []
    }
]

