[
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Mills's fault seeding technique estimates the number of indigenous faults remaining by using the ratio of detected seeded faults to total seeded faults as an indicator of the ratio of detected indigenous faults to total indigenous faults.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "The number of undiscovered seeded faults acts as an indicator of the number of total faults (including indigenous, nonseeded ones) remaining in the program.That is, the ratio of seeded faults detected to total seeded faults should be the same as the ratio of nonseeded faults detected to total nonseeded faults:",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Given that 50 faults have been seeded, 40 seeded faults have been detected, and 70 faults in total have been detected, the number of indigenous faults detected is 70 - 40 = 30.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Using Mills's formula, the estimate of the number of indigenous faults remaining is calculated as: (Number of indigenous faults detected) * (Number of seeded faults not detected) / (Number of seeded faults detected).",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "The number of undiscovered seeded faults acts as an indicator of the number of total faults (including indigenous, nonseeded ones) remaining in the program.That is, the ratio of seeded faults detected to total seeded faults should be the same as the ratio of nonseeded faults detected to total nonseeded faults:",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "Substituting the values: indigenous faults detected = 30, seeded faults not detected = 50 - 40 = 10, seeded faults detected = 40, the estimate is 30 * 10 / 40 = 7.5 indigenous faults remaining.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "Therefore, the Mills estimate of the total number of indigenous faults remaining is 7.5.",
        "citations": []
    }
]

