[
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The slack time for an activity is the amount of time that the activity can be delayed without delaying the project completion.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "To find the slack time for the activity starting at milestone F, we first identify the paths through the activity graph and their durations.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet_intro",
        "segment": "The paths and their durations are:",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "A-B-D-F-H-I-K: 7 + 2 + 6 + 2 + 1 + 10 = 28 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "A-C-E-G-H-I-K: 5 + 3 + 10 + 4 + 1 + 10 = 33 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "bullet",
        "segment": "A-C-E-G-J-K: 5 + 3 + 10 + 10 + 5 = 33 days",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The critical path is the longest path, which is 33 days (A-C-E-G-H-I-K or A-C-E-G-J-K).",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The activity starting at milestone F is F-H, which takes 2 days. The earliest start for F is after D, which is after B, which is after A. The path to F is A-B-D-F, which takes 7 + 2 + 6 = 15 days.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "From F, the path to the end is F-H-I-K, which takes 2 + 1 + 10 = 13 days. So the total duration through F is 15 + 13 = 28 days.",
        "citations": []
    },
    {
        "role": "paragraph",
        "segment": "The slack time for the activity starting at milestone F is the difference between the critical path length and the path length through F: 33 - 28 = 5 days.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "img",
                "content": null,
                "img_id": "query_evidence"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "Therefore, the slack time for the activity starting at milestone F is 5 days.",
        "citations": []
    }
]

